scenes.description: Amelia does jumping jacks while Mumei and Ollie cheer her on.
Amelia performs 'The Thinker' pose at Mumei's request.
Ollie requests a 20-second plank, which Amelia performs in a meme-style.
Amelia thanks Mumei and Ollie as they depart from the 3D studio.
Amelia interacts with Bubba and explains that the treats on the floor are Super Chats.
Amelia performs a 'Kabe-don' pose for the chat.
